 x DONE

Plot
 o palette
 x plot title
 x plot title font
 o enable/disable (0/0) marker
 x zoombase

Curves
 x lines (style, width, color)
 x symbols (type, size, color, filled)
 o error bars (style, width, color)
   alternatively: no error bars but continuous "error tube"
 x legend label
 x scaling factor (x-axis)
 x offset (y-axis)

For each axis
 x enable/disable axis label (note: empty label implies "disabled")
 x axis label
 x axis label font

Ticks
 o enable/disable ticks
 x enable/disable tick labels
 x tick values (at least: from, to, spacing)
 x tick label font

Legend
 o enable/disable legend completely
 x legend font
 x legend position (?)

Grid (?)
 o enable/disable grid
 o grid spacing
 o grid line style

Other
 o annotation font
 o save default settings for new plots/curves
 x anti-aliased plotting
